    "Consequently, a strategy of pre-training followed by finetuning is commonly adopted.",
    "Typically, techniques such as LoRA [87] are applied for fine-tuning the pre-trained model to align with downstream tasks, which might turn out to be diverse (e.g., NLP, computer vision).",
    "In this context, the pretrained FM should be robust and flexible enough to adapt to various downstream tasks.",
    "To achieve this goal, it is necessary to select a mixture of FMs hosted by FL participants based on their task training abilities.",
